because I am out there...

43:36.297 --> 43:39.460
color-analyzing women all the time.
Little did I know...

43:39.533 --> 43:43.162
that I was not the season
that I was telling people I was.

43:44.171 --> 43:48.403
I felt sorry for Janet.
So, to cheer her up, I let her do my colors.

43:48.475 --> 43:51.205
