46:19.193 --> 46:20.490
Pets or meat?

46:20.561 --> 46:25.191
Meaning I can buy the bunnies
to have as a pet...

46:25.899 --> 46:28.527
or I can buy them for....

46:28.602 --> 46:31.093
Meat. They're already dressed
and cleaned.

46:31.171 --> 46:34.766
I butcher the babies
when they are four or five months old.

46:34.842 --> 46:36.241
That's good.

46:36.310 --> 46:38.744
If you butcher the older ones,
like these guys...

46:38.812 --> 46:41.747
then they're stewers. They're not fryers.

46:41.815 --> 46:44.841
