50:17.898 --> 50:21.629
They get moving pretty fast.
They'll move away.

50:21.935 --> 50:23.493
They don't like the sound.

50:23.570 --> 50:25.231
They know exactly what you have.

50:25.305 --> 50:27.671
You don't have to say,
"l have a gun in my hand."

50:27.741 --> 50:30.107
They know it'll really tear them up.

50:32.479 --> 50:35.380
