51:39.813 --> 51:42.281
-I went to school, okay?
-What's going on?

51:43.183 --> 51:46.050
Someone in a heated discussion
down there, I guess.

51:46.953 --> 51:49.683
I'm going to jump you! I'll get you, man!

51:51.658 --> 51:54.593
...a staff member is a violation of that rule.

51:54.661 --> 51:57.357
I don't respect you!

51:57.430 --> 51:59.921
When you give me respect, I'll respect you.

52:00.300 --> 52:02.097
-Take it easy.
-I know my rights!

52:08.508 --> 52:12.137
I really don't know the answer.
I feel sorry for people...

52:12.712 --> 52:17.046
but you can't help them. I mean,
you have such a good welfare program.

52:17.484 --> 52:19.782
So, they just don't want to work.

52:19.853 --> 52:23.084
I don't think so. I really don't know.

52:25.292 --> 52:27.260
-Good shot.
